    echo -e "${WHT}│${RST}  ${RED}██╔═══██╗${GRN}██╔══██╗    ${YLW}██║   ██║${BLU}██╔══██╗${MAG}██╔══██╗    ${CYN}██╔══██╗${RED}██╔══██╗${GRN}████╗  ██║${YLW}██╔════╝${BLU}██║${RST}   ${WHT}│${RST}"
    echo -e "${WHT}│${RST}  ${RED}██║   ██║${GRN}██████╔╝    ${YLW}██║   ██║${BLU}██║  ██║${MAG}██████╔╝    ${CYN}██████╔╝${RED}███████║${GRN}██╔██╗ ██║${YLW}█████╗  ${BLU}██║${RST}   ${WHT}│${RST}"
